version_description: This is The Temper Trap's cover version of Unknown Mortal Orchestra's song. It differs in the key, lyrics and instrumentals. I have also included a Capo 2 version, for ease of playing.
Acoustic version of "Need Your Love" from the Temper Trap Acoustic Sessions, 2013.
This version contains the correct lyrics and is simplified for playing further up the neck.
Different chords, more detail in the initial part of the song.

song_name: Where Do We Go From Here

version_description: This should allow you to play along with the original. Transpose (-1) and play with capo 1 for simpler chords.
